  section#content.content
    h1 Try2Help Charity
    p.lead Dedicated to feeding the homeless, providing essentials like clothing and blankets, and ensuring financial transparency to maximize every donation's impact.
    hr
    .row
      .col-md-6
        h2 Faith in Action: Providing Hope, Help, and Healing
        p Try2Help (T2H) is a nonprofit outreach ministry dedicated to demonstrating Christ’s love by providing food, clothing, and essential support to those in need, inspired by Matthew 25:35. As part of the San Antonio Baruch Hashem Congregation, T2H operates with a commitment to service, compassion, and community support while maintaining full compliance with 501(c)(3) nonprofit regulations.
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://tblcwebsitestorage.blob.core.windows.net/pdfs/STATEMENT%20OF%20FAITH.pdf?sp=r&st=2024-09-11T03:34:42Z&se=2025-03-01T12:34:42Z&spr=https&sv=2022-11-02&sr=b&sig=x6NSFTo26VWIUjbj2N47uiGVuMuB2Q1JCGSNfZSAMqU%3D', role='button') Our Purpose »
      .col-md-6
        h2 Born from Need, Built on Faith, Growing in Service
        p Try2Help was founded in response to a critical need for better management of resources and reliable volunteer support in serving the homeless community. Emerging as an outreach ministry of Baruch Hashem Congregation, it was established with the support of Rabbi Roi Garcia and led by Robert Johnson, who initiated structural development, financial transparency, and volunteer coordination to create a sustainable and impactful organization.
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://tblcwebsitestorage.blob.core.windows.net/pdfs/TBLC%20BarCharts%20to%2023.pdf?sp=r&st=2024-09-26T02:59:09Z&se=2025-04-01T10:59:09Z&spr=https&sv=2022-11-02&sr=b&sig=BMypUqiS0gfGhGPoKldPliBbQADAI9lUMrBoOXqNCIs%3D', role='button') Our History »
      .col-md-6
        h2 Serving with Love, Giving with Integrity, United in Faith
        p Try2Help is a Christian outreach ministry dedicated to serving the homeless and those in need by providing food, clothing, and support, inspired by Matthew 25:35. Committed to transparency and accountability, Try2Help operates with open financial records and a mission to unite believers across congregations in the shared goal of compassionate service.
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://tblcwebsitestorage.blob.core.windows.net/pdfs/Article%2024%20TxPropTax.pdf?sp=r&st=2024-12-10T17:22:51Z&se=2025-04-02T00:22:51Z&spr=https&sv=2022-11-02&sr=b&sig=kOBC4dhB7DeQQRSNb6R4LW1emr93Pt71%2FY%2FeVsrnEpY%3D', role='button') Our Mission »
      .col-md-6
        h2 Order with Purpose: Biblical Principles, Fair Decisions, Strong Leadership
        p Try2Help follows Robert’s Rules of Order (RONR) as its foundational parliamentary guide to ensure structured, fair, and transparent decision-making within the organization. Rooted in biblical principles of order, accountability, and collective governance, these rules help facilitate respectful discussions, efficient leadership, and responsible stewardship as Try2Help serves those in need.
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://tblcwebsitestorage.blob.core.windows.net/pdfs/Tim%20Johnson%20Comment.pdf?sp=r&st=2024-09-11T03:38:12Z&se=2025-03-01T12:38:12Z&spr=https&sv=2022-11-02&sr=b&sig=0Jy2XLOp4hoczEoblmjTan9GAjjwWFLCFssLvJzN1B0%3D', role='button') Our Parlimentary Rules »
      .col-md-6
        h2 Guided by Faith, Governed with Purpose: The Heart of Try2Help
        p The Try2Help Bylaws establish the organization as an autonomous outreach ministry under the governance of Baruch Hashem Congregation, ensuring compliance with the Non-Profit Corporation Act of Texas and IRS 501(c)(3) regulations. These bylaws define Try2Help’s purpose of serving those in need, outline its operational structure, and ensure alignment with biblical principles and legal requirements for nonprofit organizations.
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://tblcwebsitestorage.blob.core.windows.net/pdfs/RXJ%2023%20Model%20Smpl%20p%20iv-3%20TBLC.pdf?sp=r&st=2024-09-12T05:16:29Z&se=2025-03-01T14:16:29Z&spr=https&sv=2022-11-02&sr=b&sig=T3FI2Iv3pqFm2cxFDOmATnprdIlPNOb9KXSpfZfNjpQ%3D', role='button') Our By-Laws »
